  "detailed_description": "Before the signal was lost the last voice heard from the Hazmat team's radio was \"unidentified entity.\" You need to create a new team to find out what's going on inside the Backrooms.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2290500/extras/747555c9c5b859969da27ef7b4b1a3eb.webp?t=1733395494\" width=611 height=40 /></span><br><br>This game is played as a team with one Backrooms Entity (Killer) player selected from a maximum of five people. There is only a multiplayer co-op mode.<br>If you have friends, this is great. Otherwise, you can join the server lobbies.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2290500/extras/2264c3d21daddf4fbdd0eebb921b4564.poster.avif?t=1733395494\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2290500/extras/2264c3d21daddf4fbdd0eebb921b4564.webm?t=1733395494\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2290500/extras/2264c3d21daddf4fbdd0eebb921b4564.mp4?t=1733395494\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2290500/extras/0bbc3b948cf3461395c4581806c607f9.webp?t=1733395494\" width=611 height=40 /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2290500/extras/94af0557dbd06bbfcb81055693e1fffa.webp?t=1733395494\" width=611 height=40 /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2290500/extras/0db8bcdf67f78601841c8f4387094997.webp?t=1733395494\" width=611 height=40 /></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Some Features</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"> <li> Survivor: Use vents to evade the Entity. (Movement + press Shift)<br> </li><li> Survivor: To revive your team (press F)<br> </li><li> Killer: To disguise yourself: Use the tripods around you.</li></ul><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Future update plans</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"> <li> More new maps,<br> </li><li> More entities and perks<br> </li><li> Searchable items for each map (Thermometer, Med-kit etc.)</li></ul>",
